\c 23
\s UJesu usola ababhali labaFarisi
\p
\v 1 Khona uJesu wakhuluma emaxukwini lakubafundi bakhe\x + Mark. 12.38-40. Luka 20.45-47. Luka 11.39-52.\x*,
\v 2 esithi: Ababhali labaFarisi bahlezi esihlalweni sikaMozisi;
\v 3 ngakho konke lokhu abalitshela khona ukuthi likugcine, \add ku\add*gcineni li\add kw\add*enze; kodwa lingenzi njengokwemisebenzi yabo\x + Ezra 7.10.\x*, ngoba bayakhuluma bangenzi\x + Roma 2.19-23.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba bayabopha imithwalo enzima njalo elukhuni ukuthwalwa, ba\add yi\add*beke emahlombe abantu, kodwa kabafuni ukuyisusa ngomunwe wabo\x + Luka 11.46.Seb. 15.10.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo imisebenzi yabo yonke bayenza ukuze babonwe ngabantu\x + 6.1.6.2,5,16.\x*; ngoba benza \w amafilakteriyu\w** abo abe banzi\x + Eks. 13.9.\x*, njalo bakhulisa intshaka zezembatho zabo\x + Nani 15.38. Mat. 9.20.\x*;
\v 6 bathanda izihlalo zabahloniphekayo ekudleni kwantambama\x + Mark. 12.38,39. Luka 20.46.\x*, lezihlalo eziqakathekileyo emasinagogeni\x + Luka 11.43.\x*,
\v 7 lokubingelelwa emidangeni\x + Luka 11.43.\x*\x + Mark. 12.38,39. Luka 20.46.\x*, lokubizwa ngabantu \add ngokuthi\add*: \w Rabi\w**, Rabi\x + Joha. 1.38.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Kodwa lina kalingabizwa \add ngokuthi\add* Rabi\x + Jak. 3.1.\x*; ngoba munye ongumfundisi wenu, uKristu\x + 23.10. Joha. 13.13.\x*; njalo lina lonke lingabazalwane.
\v 9 Futhi lingabizi muntu emhlabeni \add ngokuthi\add* nguyihlo\x + 1 Tim. 1.2. Tit. 1.4.\x*; ngoba munye onguYihlo, osemazulwini\x + Mal. 1.6. Mat.7.11.\x*;
\v 10 kalingabizwa \add ngokuthi ling\add*abafundisi\x + 23.8.\x*; ngoba munye ongumfundisi wenu, uKristu\x + 23.8.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa omkhulu kini\x + Mark. 9.35.\x* uzakuba yinceku yenu\x + 20.26.\x*.
\v 12 Lalowo oziphakamisayo, uzathotshiswa; lalowo ozithobayo, uzaphakanyiswa\x + Luka 14.11; 18.14. Hez. 21.26. Zaga 29.23.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Kodwa maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi\x + 23.14,15,16,23,25,27,29.\x*, ngoba livalela abantu umbuso wamazulu; ngoba kalingeni lina, labangenayo kalibavumeli ukuthi bangene\x + Luka 11.52.\x*.
\v 14 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi, ngoba lidla izindlu zabafelokazi, langokuzenzisa lenza imikhuleko emide; ngakho lizakwemukela ukulahlwa okukhulu\x + Mark. 12.40. Luka 20.47.\x*.
\v 15 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi, ngoba libhoda ulwandle lomhlaba ukuthi lenze abe munye ophendukela kumaJuda\x + Seb. 2.11; 6.5; 13.43.\x*, kuthi nxa esenziwe \add njalo\add*, limenze umntwana wesihogo ngokuphindwe kabili kulani\x + 23.33. 5.22.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Maye kini, bakhokheli abayiziphofu\x + 15.14. 23.24.\x*, abathi: Loba ngubani ofunga ngethempeli, akulutho; kodwa loba ngubani ofunga ngegolide lethempeli, ulomlandu\x + 5.33-35.\x*.
\v 17 Zithutha leziphofu\x + 23.19. 5.22.\x*! Ngoba yikuphi okukhulu, igolide, kumbe ithempeli elenza igolide libe ngcwele\x + Eks. 30.29.\x*?
\v 18 Njalo: Loba ngubani ofunga ngelathi, akulutho; kodwa loba ngubani ofunga ngomnikelo ophezu kwalo\x + 15.5.\x*, ulomlandu.
\v 19 Zithutha leziphofu! Ngoba yikuphi okukhulu\x + 23.17.\x*, umnikelo, kumbe ilathi elenza umnikelo ube ngcwele\x + Eks. 29.37. Mat. 5.23.\x*?
\v 20 Ngakho ofunga ngelathi ufunga ngalo langakho konke okuphezu kwalo;
\v 21 lofunga ngethempeli ufunga ngalo langaye ohlala kulo\x + 1 Kho. 8.13. 2 Lan. 6.2. Hlab. 26.8; 132.14.\x*;
\v 22 lofunga ngezulu ufunga ngesihlalo sobukhosi sikaNkulunkulu langaye ohlala phezu kwaso\x + 5.34. Hlab. 11.4.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi, ngoba lithela okwetshumi kwetshwayi leganga \w ledile\w** \w lekhumini\w**\x + Luka 11.42.\x*; liyekele okunzima komlayo, ukwahlulela lesihawu lokholo; belifanele ukwenza lezizinto, lingaziyekeli lalezo\x + 1 Sam. 15.22. Mat. 9.13; 12.7.\x*.
\v 24 Bakhokheli abayiziphofu\x + 23.16.\x*, likhetha umiyane, kodwa liginye ikamela\x + 19.24.\x*.
\v 25 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi, ngoba lihlambulula ingaphandle\x + Luka 11.39.\x* yenkezo leyomganu, kodwa ngaphakathi kugcwele ukuphanga\x + Mark. 7.4.\x* lobuhwaba\x + 1 Kor.7.5.\x*.
\v 26 MFarisi oyisiphofu! Hlambulula kuqala ingaphakathi yenkezo leyomganu, ukuze kuhlambuluke lengaphandle yakho\x + Mark. 7.4.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi\x + Luka 11.44.\x*, ngoba lifanana lamangcwaba aconjwe aba mhlophe, abonakala emahle ngaphandle, kanti ngaphakathi agcwele amathambo abafileyo\x + Seb. 23.3.\x* lokungcola konke\x + Nani 19.16.\x*.
\v 28 Kunjalo lani ngaphandle libonakala ebantwini lilungile, kanti ngaphakathi ligcwele ukuzenzisa lobubi.
\p
\v 29 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi, ngoba lakha amangcwaba abaprofethi\x + Luka 11.47,48.\x*, licecise amangcwaba abalungileyo\x + 12.44; 25.7. Luka 11.25. Isam. 21.2,19.\x*,
\v 30 lithi: Uba besikhona ensukwini zabobaba bethu, besingayikuhlanganyela labo egazini labaprofethi.
\v 31 Kunjalo liyazifakazela lina ukuthi lingamadodana alabo ababulala abaprofethi\x + Seb. 7.51,52. 1 Thes. 2.15.\x*;
\v 32 lina-ke gcwalisani\x + Gen. 15.16. Dan. 8.23. 1 Thes. 2.16.\x* isilinganiso saboyihlo\x + 7.2.\x*!
\v 33 Zinyoka, nzalo yamabululu\x + 3.7; 12.34.\x*, lizaphepha njani ukulahlwa kwesihogo\x + 23.15.\x*?
\p
\v 34 Ngakho, khangelani, mina ngithuma kini abaprofethi labahlakaniphileyo\x + Luka 11.49-51.\x* lababhali\x + 13.52.\x*; l\add abanye\add* babo lizababulala libabethele\x + 5.12; 21.35. 2 Lan. 36.16.\x*; l\add abanye\add* lizabatshaya ngesiswepu emasinagogeni\x + 10.17.\x* enu libazingele imizi ngemizi\x + 10.23.\x*;
\v 35 ukuze kwehlele phezu kwenu igazi lonke elilungileyo elachithwa emhlabeni\x + Isam. 18.24.\x*, kusukela egazini likaAbela olungileyo\x + Gen. 4.8.\x*, kuze kufike egazini likaZakariya\x + 2 Lan. 24.20,21.\x* indodana kaBarakiya\x + 2 Lan. 24.22. Zek. 1.1.\x*, elambulala phakathi kwethempeli\x + 1 Kho. 6.2. Luka 11.51.\x* lelathi\x + Eks. 40.6,29. 2 Kho. 16.14. Hez. 40.47.\x*.
\v 36 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Zonke lezizinto zizakwehlela phezu kwalesisizukulwana.
\s UJesu ukhalela iJerusalema
\p
\v 37 Jerusalema, Jerusalema\x + Luka 13.34,35.\x*, wena obulala abaprofethi\x + 21.35.\x* njalo obakhanda ngamatshe labo abathunywe kuwe\x + 21.35.\x*! Bengithanda kangakanani ukubuthela ndawonye abantwana bakho, njengesikhukhukazi sibuthela amatsiyane aso\x + Dute. 32.11,12.\x* ngaphansi kwempiko, kodwa kalivumanga\x + Ruthe 2.12.\x*.
\v 38 Khangelani, indlu yenu itshiyiwe kini ilunxiwa.
\v 39 Ngoba ngithi kini: Kalisoze langibona kusukela khathesi, lize lithi: Ubusisiwe ozayo ebizweni leNkosi\x + Hlab. 118.26. Luka 13.35.\x*.
